1:35:19.333 --> 1:35:20.958
♪ …years I roamed ♪

1:35:22.083 --> 1:35:25.000
♪ I gazed a gazeless stare… ♪

1:35:27.291 --> 1:35:28.291
[Christine] Cindy…

1:35:30.125 --> 1:35:31.125
my sister…

1:35:32.125 --> 1:35:35.041
