1:35:58.791 --> 1:35:59.791
it's real.

1:36:01.875 --> 1:36:03.416
[Christine] I thought he was different.

1:36:04.125 --> 1:36:05.916
I thought he would believe me.

1:36:07.208 --> 1:36:09.333
But Nick had a destiny in this town.

1:36:10.333 --> 1:36:13.541
And you don't become sheriff
talking about ghost stories.

1:36:13.625 --> 1:36:16.458
♪ We never lost control… ♪

1:36:17.458 --> 1:36:19.125
What the hell happened here?

1:36:21.625 --> 1:36:24.666
-Tommy Slater.
-♪ With the man who sold the world…♪

1:36:25.208 --> 1:36:26.416
He just went crazy.

1:36:28.500 --> 1:36:30.125
[Kapinski] Fucking Shadysiders.

1:36:34.791 --> 1:36:36.625
